game.name: Princess Wedding Cake
game.description:
One of the best recreational activities available online, Princess Wedding Cake is meant for kids of all ages. Your primary job in this awesome free online cooking game is to decorate a beautiful cake and make it more delicious for princess Elsa. The wedding occasion has just reached and the princess wants to prepare a cake for it, but did not. Help the wonderful girl to get the cake prepared on time and make her feel special.

Elsa is a very famous character right from the animated movie Frozen and now she needs your help. The good news is that she has a plan to get engaged with a handsome Jack Frost, so she wants to surprise him with her fabulous cooking and creativity skills. All you need to pay attention towards the details while creating the scrumptious cake for Princess Elsa and Jack Frost in this cool flash game. Your valuable assistance is enough to make them look happy souls on their big day. 

In this latest kids game, you will also have an opportunity to save or print the picture in case if you do your best and get the delicious cake prepared perfectly. This way you will be able to show your talent to your family or friends. Use the right ingredients and tools to prepare the mouth-watering wedding cake for Elsa and Jack. Your imagination and creativity will show you a way to create a perfect wedding cake and bring a long smile on the face of Princess Elsa, who will always be grateful to you.
